* On accordion block, icon position has 4 vales, left, right, extreme right and extreme left. The first two, position the icon relative to the button text. The latter, position the icons relative to the button box, independent of the text. Keep in mind the text alignemnt changes (left, center, right), and the icon positioning should keep this in ming. Aldo, add box-border: size-box ont he button tittle 


